body:
Here it is.

They thought they could do something. They were wrong. And now people are castigating them for &#039;stringing them along&#039; and &#039;breaking their promises.&#039;

Now, let&#039;s be perfectly honest here: They should have communicated better. They shouldn&#039;t have taken this long to make a definite statement. But this reaction they&#039;re getting is exactly WHY they took this long: they wanted to make sure, 100%, that they wouldn&#039;t be able to implement solo queue in a way that they&#039;re happy with.
